AD | This week I headed back to my birth state of Colorado with #deltafaucet to tour the @hgtv Dream Home 2023, and what a dream indeed! From its picturesque views and beautiful mountain-tucked location, to the deliciously inspiring interior color and perfectly integrated #sneakystorage throughout, this Dream Home may just be the best one yet! The way @bpatrickflynn brilliantly included all the gorgeous and highly functional @deltafaucet innovations is truly a Masterclass in designing a home that is not only joyful, but also super hard working. I didn’t want to leave! Thank you so much #deltafaucet for having me. 

Now if you need me I’ll be in the uber moody coffee room…or maybe the tucked in the book nook…or out on the deck…or maybe in the garage 😅 #hgtvdreamhome #coloradodreaming #hgtv

Hi friends!!! Hope you all have been having a great weekend. I’ve been having the BEST time here in Colorado and the fun isn’t quite over yet! Don’t miss out on an exclusive live tour of the #HGTVDreamHome 2023 with me  @bpatrickflynn and @veluxusa  Tomorrow, Monday Dec 5 at 1:30 pm ET. Set your alarms! See you there😊

Closing out my trip to beautiful Colorado with a design convo and tour of the @hgtv Dream Home 2023 with its brilliant designer @bpatrickflynn . We talk about all the amazing @veluxusa skylights throughout the house and how they inspired the colors and overall design of the home.
Tooth drama, design pivots and color adventures. This fireside chat with @bpatrickflynn might be my fave part of the @hgtv Dream Home 2023 tour.

The holidays are in full swing (even though we haven’t started decorating yet😅) and that means it’s guests-on-rotation season. I LOVE hosting guests overnight, but as a small home dweller it can be a challenge. I partnered with @westelm to share some inspiring ideas for how to create a comfortable and inviting space for all those overnight visitors this season. Click the link in my bio for the full article! 📷: @alannahale #westelmpartner #mywestelm

How many of you were around when Naomi and I mounted our last TV on the wall? It’s actually how #pivotabitch was birthed😅. We are basically pros at this point! I’ve envisioned creating a big floor to ceiling gallery wall surrounding a frame tv in our living room for a couple of years now. Its finally underway. #thecottagebungalow #smallhomebigstyle #ourhomestyle

Finally starting to deck the halls in #thecottagebungalow for the holiday season! When it comes to holiday decorating I have two ironclad rules: 1. We never decorate before Dec 15. And 2. Always, always, always with fresh greenery. Cedar garland is my absolute favorite. Ive been using it since we moved into our home 8 years ago. I usually always get it from Costco (you can order it online too!), but I also love the wreaths and garlands from @lynchcreekfarm . The key to keeping it looking great longer is the 24 hr soak. I always soak it for at least 24 hrs and let it dry outside for a bit before hanging. A daily spritz of water freshens it as well. Happy Holidays friends! #deckthehalls #freshgarland

2022 was a really really difficult year for me emotionally. I felt like I was in a grief fog the entire year. 2021 brought gut wrenching loss and 2022 brought the grief aftermath. Not only was I ready for the fog to lift, but I was ready for a pretty radical change. I always told myself I was cutting my locs at 40 (i turned 40 in May #teamtaurus). After 12 years it’s time for a new journey. Thank you so so much @barberdej for your care and energy😘😘. Happy New Year friends!! May 2023 bring you all a multitude of blessings and life changing joy! Also I just realized none of you have EVER seen me without my locs. I was already a couple years into the journey when I started my blog 🥰.

Hey hey friends! Here’s Part 2 of our FrameTV gallery wall project. We got our media console over the holidays and I’m OB-SESSSSSSED. It’s the Simone console designed by my bestie @carmeonhamilton as part of her furniture collection she designed with @tovfurniture. It was a #pivotabitch and it was WORTTTTHHH ITTTT!!! It’s so good and I can’t even imagine anything else here now. The size and scale is perfect to anchor the oversized nature of the art that will go on the wall. Speaking of…the art has started to ship and arrive so Part 3 is coming up soon. #thecottagebungalow #smallhomeboldstyle #moodyinteriors #eclecticinteriors #frametv #frametvgallerywall

I get asked at least 5x a day about my skincare routine so I thought I’d share it with you on this rainy stormy Saturday. THIS IS MY CURRENT MORNING routine. Ive tried a lot of things and this is what my skin is liking at the moment. Many of these products I’ve been using for a very long time, while others are newer to me. I’m testing out @sundayriley specifically. I’ve ALWAYS been a huge advocate for skin first when it comes to beauty, and now that I’m 40 this is even MOREso the case. I’m ALWAYS gonna tell you to remember your sunscreen. EVERY. SINGLE. DAY. Also FYI- my skin is fairly sensitive and dry. I’m also not acne prone so everything I use is very specific to my skin type and what works for me. I like quite a dewey natural look, even when wearing makeup so I tend to be heavy on the moisture. I think that’s about it. If you have any questions that haven’t been answered in the video leave them in the comments and I got you:) #skincareroutine #morningskincareroutine #skincaredaily #skincaredailyroutine #over40skincareroutine #over40skincare

Hey hey friends! As a follow up to my morning routing I shared earlier this week here’s (on of my) current evening skincare routines. I interchange putting on my oil before or after my moisturizer depending on my mood. Oftentimes i mix them together and apply them at the same time. #erasetheday #nightimeskincareroutine #nightimeskincare #eveningskincareroutine #eveningskincare #over40skincare

The art for our gallery wall has arrived and it’s honestly better than Christmas morning! Thank you so much @framebridge for this moment of pure joy! So excited to get these hung. #partner #thecottagebungalow #ourdownsizingjourney #smallhomebigstyle #framebridge

3 things: 1. The Frame TV gallery wall is complete……for now!! It’s already changed since filming this😅. It’s a constantly evolving situation over here. 2. Bestie’s furniture is sturdy AF, but def don’t stand on your furniture. Use a ladder or step stool😅. 3. This was such a fun project to put together and I love seeing all of the different pieces I’ve collected over the years finally on display in our home. Thank you so much @framebridge for helping this come to life. #thecottagebungalow #smallhomebigstyle #gallerywall #gallerywallinspo

If you take nothing else with you from me, please let it be this. Curating a home you intend to live in and have longevity in is a marathon, not a sprint. It takes time. It’s not a race. Do it thoughtfully, intentionally and with care. Like our lives, our homes evolve and change. Home means something different to all of us. Let yours reflect your unique vision, story and evolution. You don’t have to do what everyone else is doing. Do you boo! Also try to enjoy it at every stage….even when it’s not quite where you want it to be. Thanks for coming to my TED talk. #thecottagebungalow #ourdownsizingjourney #smallhomebigstyle #smallhomeboldstyle #smallhomestyle #electicinteriors

Because BIG TAURUS ENERGY!! You’ve been warned. The #shavondamademedoit squad can attest😅😂. BUUUTTT to be fair…. I’m only ever going to influence the really really good stuff because I love youuuuuu and you deserve beautiful things that bring you joy. And also because #buyoncebuywell!! This @audiotechnicausa record player is a good one so go ahead and add to cart!☺️#thecottagebungalow #smallhomebigstyle #smallhomeboldstyle

Nighttime views in #thecottagebungalow are the best views tbh. Also I get asked often how the kitchen relates to the rest of the living area since we widened the entry in the renovation. Here ya go. Fun fact: I legit freaked out when I first saw how wide it was. I almost called my contractor the next day to have him come close it back up a bit. But then I slept on it and felt better in the morning. This is bout as close to open-concept as I’m ever gonna get.😅 It’s just not my jam. Happy weekend friends! #thecottagebungalow #ourdownsizingjourney #smallhomebigstyle #smallhomeboldstyle #smallhomestyle #smallhomeliving #eclecticstyle #moodyinteriors

LISSSSENN. One thing’s for certain and two thing’s are for sure….when it comes to a lamp IMMA BUY IT! And I’m going to play lamp roulette until I find the perfect place for them all. I ordered these two at the same time but this one just arrived yesterday. Y’all. THIS ONE RIGHT HEEEEREEEE. This the one. The black scrunch lamp is also bae and it moved to the office where it’s equally as amazing. Lamps and rugs-they have me in a chokehold. I can’t NOT buy the lamp. My garage is proof😅. On a serious note: if you’re looking to refresh your space and you can only focus on ONE area Im ALWAYS going to tell you to invest in lighting. It can monumentally change a space and it’s low commitment. No matter your style or budget great lighting is magical. Remember to layer it: general, task, ambient. #thecottagebungalow #ourdownsizingjourney #smallhomeliving #smallhomebigstyle #smallhomeboldstyle #moodyinteriors #eclectichome

😫😫😫I swear it’s coming friends😅. Remember that marathon we keep talking about 😂. The good news is the interior is complete and I’m working in here everyday now. Having this space is better than I could’ve hoped for. I can’t wait to show you how I’ve brought this space together. #sgstylexstudioshed #officestudio #studioshed #backyardoffice #backyardofficespace

See the way my ADHD works is like I usually come up with the best ideas when I’m in the middle of one thing and I’m supposed to be paying attention to what’s happening at that moment🥴. I was fully in the middle something when I remembered seeing my friend @mrorlandosoria use lanterns next to a console in front of his gallery wall and thinking it was a viiiiiibe. So here we are. Thank you Orlando for the inspiration.😘 Now if I can only remember what the heck I was doing before this stroke of genius hit. 🤔 🤷🏿‍♀️. #thecottagebungalow #smallhomebigstyle #moodyinteriors #eclectichome #pocketsofmyhome #interiorstyling

Once these candles get lit dont ask me to do nuthin. 🗣️GET SOMEBODY ELSE TO DO IT. Also we’re not gonna talk about the fact that Naomi accidentally broke my match cloche😩😭. But we still bout to use it though 😌#thecottagebungalow #smallhomeboldstyle #smallhomeliving #moodyinteriors #eclectichome #eclecticinteriors

Callie got a new bed and now she’s about to be on even more of her #middlemanagement BS than she usually is😩😅. Also can we get a little commotion for this dog bed though. It’s haaaaard out here to find a dog bed for a Dane that is stylish, comfortable AND big enough! Technically this is a bed meant for pups to be able to snuggle in with their humans, but it also just works for those of us with big ass dogs too! It’s the PupCloud Human-Size Memory Foam Dog Bed. We bought it for her for Christmas from @paworiginal and it just arrived today. We’ve already purchased two beds from them before so it’s a brand I recommend as a repeat customer. Will keep you updated as she uses it over time. ALSO my heart can’t handle the Naomi + Callie duo. Honestly it’s just too much💜💜.
New week. New flowers. Happy Monday friends! #weeklyindulgence #thecottagebungalow #freshflowersmakemehappy #blackgirlsloveflowers #pocketofmyhome
Answering a most frequently asked question: why i cut the stamens out of my lilies. 1. Extend their vase life 2. They aren’t needed inside 3. Miss the mess.
These are Helebores by the way😅😫🙄. Somebody please come get y’all’s friend. #thecottagebungalow #navondaconversations

Welcome to our first project of 2023. #projectthebombcyclonemadeusdoit 😩. It wasn’t planned but Mother Nature said 🗣️YOU THOUGHT. And here we are. We are already making some interesting discoveries. Old homes really are the best and also a pain in the neck at the same time. 😩 #thecottagebungalow #oldhouseproblems #smallhomeliving #oldhouselove #renovationproject

Tis the season for me to drag my wife all around town to clip blooming branches from the side of the road! One of my favorite things about living in Sacramento is how abundant the offerings are for foraging. I always anticipate the early spring Acacia blooms. Taking advantage because the cold wet weather is headed back into town next week—-allegedly😅. Happy Weekend ahead Friends! #thecottagebungalow #weeklyindulgence #springblooms #springforaging #mymoodyhome

AD| One of my goals for the year is to try more new recipes and I’m excited to partner with @testkitchen to do just that! I’m trying my hand at their Vegan Almost Hands-Free Mushroom Risotto recipe for the first time, and even as a risotto newbie America’s Test Kitchen and its resources helps me feel confident in the kitchen. Click the link in my bio or go to AmericasTestKitchen.com/Shavonda for my special insider membership offer for full digital access to the kitchen plus their great magazines!  #americastestkitchen

#projectthebombcyclonemadeusdoit is well underway friends. Week 1 of work included: demo, discovering more hidden windows 😅, raising the ceiling height as much as possible (a whopping 2-5 inches that feels like 2-5 feet tbh), added outlets (we only had 1 functioning outlet in this room for 8 years 😩), roughed in for pendants and overhead lighting (a marriage compromise), got rid of the dreaded sidelites (Hallefreakinlujah!!), shortened the width of the step into the room, installed drywall, floated the first coat of mud and fixed the roof. This room already feels SO. MUCH. BETTER. Still lots to do but really excited about the progress. Sharing daily updates, in depth details and behind the scenes in stories. You can get caught up in the highlight. #thecottagebungalow #ourdownsizingjourney #itsamarathonnotasprint #renovationlife #renovationproject #oldhouselove #oldhouseproblems #smallhomebigstyle #smallhomedesign

I do my best work at night….and in sweats apparently😅Rearranged the gallery wall a bit and added this gorgeous piece from @bananarepublic to the mix. Yup, THAT Banana Republic! They are launching a home collection and have introduced a curated collection of art. I was so drawn to this piece by @marinacano and her capture of these beautiful animals together. It’s titled “Necking Under the Storm” and when I saw it I immediately thought of Naomi. A visual representation of our marriage and how we always face whatever is headed our way together. It definitely felt like this belonged in our home. Fun fact: giraffes are my fave animal☺️. Also, most of our house is sitting under a layer of drywall dust and I just needed a moment create some order within the chaos. #gifted #thecottagebungalow #gallerywallinspo #smallhomebigstyle #moodyinteriors

Black History Month might be over, but the celebration of Black voices, businesses and experiences is 365 around here! I recently partnered with @toyotausa to participate in their #blackhistorybookswap and it was EVERYTHING! This event centered Black creatives, businesses and authors, and I loved every minute of it. We were each asked to bring a book to discuss and share with the others and I brought Aphrophic: Celebrating the Legacy of the Black Family Home by @aphrochic (purchased at @marcus.books ). Toyota provided me with the all-new 2023 Toyota Camry to experience for the week and to take to the event, and now I want a new car 😅. I loved meeting the other creatives and discussing  the books they brought and why they felt called to share them. This was actually such a fun twist on a book club and a great way to get to know new people, too! Delicious organic food was provided by @thefoodiedoula and the swap was hosted at beautiful @sip.alkalirye . This was such an amazing event and I’m so excited to add these books to my library. I’m super inspired to host my own book swap now. Who all comin? #sponsored #camry

Issa update! The next phase of #projectthebombcyclonemadeusdoit is complete! We set the foundation for the flooring to be installed, and I decided to install tongue and groove wood planks on the ceiling. In a perfect world we would have an original wood beam ceiling, but this is an affordable and easy alternative to give us a bit of texture and visual interest in the space. I’m really happy with how it turned out. Honestly just having the paneling gone is SUUUUUCH an improvement. Paint and flooring is up next! And yes, we are painting the wood ceiling the same color as the walls…#thecottagebungalow #ourdownsizingjourney #smallhomebigstyle #renovationproject #homerenovation #bedroomremodel #tongueandgrooveceiling

A couple of years ago this was all a dream and today it’s a beautiful reality! For years bestie and I have been trying to figure out a way to organize and execute unique meetups with you and @trovatrip gave us the incredible opportunity to do so while traveling to some of the most beautiful places in the world! My heart is so full and words can’t express how truly grateful I am to get to do this with my best friend @carmeonhamilton  What a life!! Having the best time getting to know these amazing folks who came from all over to experience Pura Vida with us! #carmondaxcostarica #trovatrip

#projectthebombcyclonemadeusdoit progress: floooooooorrrrrring daaaay and @stugastudio Lucia is looking (and feeling) REAL good! We are sooooo close to being done with this room friends. Happy weekend everyone! #stugastudio #stugastudiopartner #thecottagebungalow #renovationjourney #renovationproject #primarybedroomrenovation

Issa Update!!!! #projectthebombcyclonemadeusdoit is moving right along friends! We have floors and we have paint AND I AM OBSESSSSSSSED with both. 🤎🤎🤎 We are soooo close to moving back in here and  I can’t wait. My back is ready for my mattress again 😩 and we are both ready to not have to dig through totes for our clothes anymore! Up next we are building out our new “dressing area”. Have you been following the closet saga?😅 Stories sees it first friends.  #thecottagebungalow #primarybedroomrenovation #moodyinteriors #smallhomebigstyle #ourdownsizingjourney #smallhomeboldstyle

Spring is finally here and to celebrate I gave #thecottagebungalow kitchen a fresh spring look with @magnolia. #ad From textiles to tableware, Magnolia’s new spring collection is SO GOOD! How incredible are these  scalloped plates and amber goblets! I mean, I’m completely obsessed! As a #buyoncebuywell advocate I LOVE that Magnolia offers heirloom quality homewares on their website that are as long lasting as they are beautiful. If you’re looking to refresh your space this spring head to the link in my bio to find the perfect pieces to add to your home story. But you better move fast, they sell out quick! #mymagnolia #thecottagebungalowkitchen #smallhomebigstyle #kitchenstyling #moodycottagestyle

In Progress: if y’all have been following the #projectthebombcyclonemadeusdoit journey on stories you already know it’s been a sagaaaaa😂. At this point every IKEA between Burbank and Emeryville knows me and Naomi on a first name basis. I wish I was lying, but I’m not🤣. This sweet old vintage waterfall vanity that I rescued from a friends barn was an unexpected find that I desperately wanted to work in here, but it’s a smidge too long for the space😭. Annnnnd we’ve spent exactly 7,654 hrs building and rebuilding wardrobes to perfect fit into our very awkward, wonky-walled, sloped ceilinged small space. But we did it! We’ve still got a bit to go before it’s done, but our very unplanned bedroom renovation is shaping up. Now the million dollar question is: WILL NAOMI’S SNEAKERS FIT? And the answer is THEY BETTER or I’m burning everything down! #thecottagebungalow #smallhomedesign #smallhomebigstyle #smallhomeboldstyle #myeclectichome #moodyhome #smallspaceliving #smallspacedesign

The evolution of the design of #sgstylestudio over several months and hairstyles😅😊. 

Building and creating this space has been a literal dream come true and a long time in the making. I remember looking out onto our very vast, empty weed infested grassy backyard and telling Naomi I’d love to have a small office back here one day. And here we are. Remember it’s a marathon, not a sprint friends. I still have to spray that amazing vintage chinoiserie mirror Facebook Marketplace find, and I have to paint and style the exterior. BUT, IM WORKING IN MY OFFICE. And I’m so incredibly grateful and beyond excited.

I’ve tagged every brand you see in the room. The “desk” is actually a console table I found at Home Goods. The credenza is two IKEA Besta units installed side by side. 90% of the room was styled with things I already owned from the Mary Poppins garage:) Design for me is ever evolving so I can’t wait to add to and edit the space over time. #sgstylestudiobuild #sgstylestudio #sgstylexstudioshed #backyardoffice #backyardstudio

Hey hey friends! How about this #smallspacebigstyle moment, huh! I worked with @veluxusa to transform this small 120 sqft home office into a multifunctional space with skylights to make it feel open and bright, took the sunny yellow color to the ceiling and added a Murphy bed for guests. Head to my stories for a closer look and then pop over to @em_henderson website for a deeper dive into the project! 📸: @rustywilliamsphoto

One thing about me: when it comes to a small space if you give me an inch imma take a mile! While it was pretty and there was absolutely nothing wrong with it, this space next to the sofa felt like a missed opportunity for our home to work just a tad bit harder for us. I had this random idea to move our bookcase storage over here and it was 100% the right decision.

At first glance you’d think there’s no way this could work (many of you doubted me😅) but I’m all about that #sneakystorage life and I knew it would. For this project I used IKEA Billy bookcases, height extensions and doors in the black brown colorway. I’m a DIE HARD Billy bookcase fan. Always will be. And while I love a good Billy built-in hack as much as the next, there’s nothing like a Billy right out of the box in its original form packed with books. 

One of my biggest #smallspaceliving tips is to use 👏🏿your 👏🏿walls, and this is the perfect example of why. This little space went from just being pretty to look at, to an area with a purpose that elevates and maximizes our lives in our little cottage. This house just keeps providing us with more than enough and I love this for us. #thecottagebungalow #smallhomeliving #smallhomebigstyle #smallhomeboldstyle #moodyinteriors #eclecticinteriors

The category is COLOR!!! When our @veluxusa Brighten Up Any Room Giveaway winner said anything goes in this space as far as the color, I said 🗣️SAY LESS! We took the color they already had on the walls (seriously such great taste!) and amplified it with bright complimentary color throughout the room. With the addition of the new Solar Powered Fresh Air Skylights this work/guest space now feels vibrant, energized and oh so fun! Head to stories for their reaction to the space!

Hey hey friends! Pool season is almost here and this year we are prepping for all the poolside hangs with @overstock exciting Memorial Day discounts! Last year was our first year with #naomispool and we quickly learned we didn’t have nearly enough loungers or umbrellas, and I refuse to not be prepared this year. It was time for a pool deck upgrade. 

I fell in love with these fab @safavieh umbrellas and loungers with wheels, adjustable backs and hidden side tables as soon as I saw them on the site. You know how much I love a #sneakystorage moment and the tables that pop out on either side are soooo good! This combo sets the perfect foundation for a summer filled with fun pool days in the sun. Head over for some awesome deals to get your outdoors summer ready. Shopping on Overstock is easy, and shipping is always free! #overstockstyle #overstockpartner #lovesafavieh #thecottagebungalowbackyardretreat
A ringing endorsement from our favorite friend Shavonda! View her namesake Garner sofa on our website and see more of her beautifully curated home at @sgardnerstyle ✨

Hey hey friends! Our backyard is feeling very Amalfi Coast meets 70s Palm Springs and I’m here for ittttt!  I have just a few more details to add and we’ll be ready for all the summer hangs. Also did you peep the cameo from  #middlemanagement 🐶. #OurArticle

The poolside umbrellas needed to be just a wee bit bigger. ⛱️⛱️. I loved the other ones so much I ordered more. But slightly different 😅. Summer is almossssst here!!! #thecottagebungalowbackyardretreat #thecottagebungalow #backyardrenovation

Y’all. Summer entered the chat WITH A VENGEANCE. It’s been HELLA HOT, which means I’ve been IN. SIDE. But we have a lil break in the heat so I’ve been taking the long route to work. Next week imma be right back on the 15 seconds from the back door route, but today I’m gonna stop and enjoy the flowers. Also…I’m really not mad at the commute either way!😊 #sgstylestudio #thecottagebungalow #backyardstudio #backyardoffice #smallhomebigstyle #backyardofficespace

Life lately. || As a creative with ADHD I’ve learned I NEED to prioritize sitting the hell down somewhere. It’s not easy because of my constant need to be “doing something”, but this past month I’ve been finding joy in slowing down and enjoying this home we’ve worked so hard to build and create over the past almost decade.
